Usage: deletePGPin [-help] [-area {x1 y1 x2 y2}]
                   [-layer <layer> | {list_of_layer}] [-net <name>] [-pg_port] [-all  | -selected ]

-help                                # Prints out the command usage
-all                                 # Specifies whether to delete all PG pins
                                     # (bool, optional)
-area {x1 y1 x2 y2}                  # Specifies the coordinates of the area
                                     # (box, optional)
-layer <layer> | {list_of_layer}     # Specifies layers (string, optional)
-net <name>                          # Specifies net name ((net)*, optional)
-pg_port                             # Specifies to delete pg port with pg
                                     # shape, or delete pg port based on
                                     # specified net name from -net option.
                                     # (bool, optional)
-selected                            # specifies whether to delete selected PG
                                     # pins (bool, optional)